---
// platform/src/components/landing/Hero.astro
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden section-padding">
  <div class="absolute inset-0"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent"/><div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-brand-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"/></div>
  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-800/80 border border-surface-700/50 mb-8 animate-fade-in"><span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span><span class="text-sm text-surface-300">Cloudflare 네이티브 WordPress 호스팅 · 100% 무료 · 무제한</span></div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 animate-slide-up"><span class="text-white">서버 없이 운영하는</span><br/><span class="gradient-text">진짜 WordPress</span></h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-surface-400 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 mb-10 animate-slide-up">Cloudflare 계정만 연결하면 몇 분 안에 워드프레스 사이트를 만들고 운영할 수 있습니다. VPS 없이, PHP-WASM으로 Edge에서 바로 실행됩니다. 익숙한 관리자 화면과 플러그인, 테마는 그대로 사용하세요.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4 animate-slide-up">
          <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-primary text-base px-8 py-4 w-full sm:w-auto"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>무료로 워드프레스 시작하기</a>
          <a href="/features" class="btn-secondary text-base px-8 py-4 w-full sm:w-auto">기능 살펴보기</a>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-lg mx-auto lg:mx-0 mt-16 animate-slide-up">
          <div><p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">1분</p><p class="text-sm text-surface-500 mt-1">워드프레스 설치</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">100%</p><p class="text-sm text-surface-500 mt-1">플러그인·테마 호환</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">0원</p><p class="text-sm text-surface-500 mt-1">서버 비용</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative animate-slide-up hidden lg:block">
        <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500/20 via-yellow-400/10 to-brand-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-xl"></div>
        <img src="/images/phone-character.png" alt="휴대폰으로 워드프레스 사이트를 관리하는 모습" class="relative w-full max-w-md mx-auto drop-shadow-2xl" loading="eager" width="640" height="640" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 animate-slide-up"><div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto"><div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500/20 via-yellow-400/10 to-brand-500/20 rounded-2xl blur-xl"></div><div class="relative glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 border-b border-surface-700/50"><div class="flex gap-1.5"><div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div><div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/60"></div><div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/60"></div></div><div class="flex-1 flex justify-center"><div class="px-4 py-1 bg-surface-800 rounded-md text-xs text-surface-500">cloud-press.co.kr/wp-admin</div></div></div><div class="aspect-video bg-surface-900 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="text-center"><div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-2xl bg-brand-500/10 flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div><p class="text-surface-400 text-sm">WordPress 관리자 대시보드</p></div></div></div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>
